        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A <em>composer staff</em> is short and shaped like an elegant black conductor's baton with a silver tip. When waved through the air, it hums melodically. In this way, you can play it as though it were an instrument, and it grants a +2 item bonus to Performance checks made with it.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Haunting Hymn]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Summon Instrument]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Concordant Choir]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Sonata Span]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Concordant Choir]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Roaring Applause]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Sculpt Sound]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
